The paper discusses a new model for class incremental learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The model involves neural networks and addresses issues related to catastrophic forgetting and softmax suppression. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
